
<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
<meta http-equiv="Content-Type" content="text/html; charset=utf-8" />
<title>CSS3 transform初体验之demo2</title>
<style type="text/css">
body{background-color:#E9E9E9; color:#333333; font-family:"Lucida handwriting",Arial,Helvetica,sans-serif; font-size:16px;}
a,a:hover{color:#333333; text-decoration:none;}
.box{width:500px; margin:100px auto 0; font-size:0.75em;}
.title{font-size:1.5em;}

#content a{display:block; width:256px; margin:60px 0 0; padding:10px 10px 15px; text-align:center; background:white; border:1px solid #bfbfbf;
-webkit-box-shadow:2px 2px 3px rgba(135, 139, 144, 0.4); -moz-box-shadow:2px 2px 3px rgba(135, 139, 144, 0.4); box-shadow:2px 2px 3px rgba(135, 139, 144, 0.4); 
-webkit-transition:all 1s ease-in;
}

#content img{display:block; width:256px; height:192px; margin-bottom:10px; border:0;}

.dd1{
border-color:#9a9a9a; -webkit-transform:rotate(120deg); -moz-transform:rotate(120deg); transform:rotate(120deg);
-webkit-transition:all 6s ease-in;
}
.dd2{
-webkit-transform:rotate(-410deg); -moz-transform:rotate(-410deg); transform:rotate(-410deg); 
-webkit-transition:all 6s ease-in;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>
<div class="box">
	<h1 class="title">CSS3旋转与盒投影+鼠标悬停效果</h1>
    <div class="content" id="content">
    	<a href="#zhangxinxu" class="pic" id="s1">
        	<img src="http://www.mhtml5.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/05/123123.png" />
            
        </a>      
    </div>
</div>
</body>
</html>
